# Large Payload Test Notebook

This notebook tests handling of large payloads (>100KB when serialized).
It verifies the base64 chunking fix works correctly.

## Size Verification

```bash {"name":"check-size"}
echo "Large payload notebook loaded successfully"
echo "This file should be >100KB when serialized"
```
